{"tid":1391590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[招募IT, 文宣, 搜集員] 全民超合作超小器運動","createTime":"2019-07-31T13:13:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T04:08:55.000Z","uid":266022,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6839330d5ae33bc228bfbb86bde25f8ddf7ab9c1","tid":1391590,"uid":266022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:13:12.000Z","msg":"我哋係一班IT中嘅小器鬼們, 目前正組隊著手開發香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歷史網頁 - 小器簿，網頁主要係針對巿民擔心警察無依法律制裁白衣人等等問題，怕高調拉人，低調放人，或輕判小罪，而我哋就係要記住佢keep住跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前缺文宣，前台UI (Reactjs, css)開發及資料搜集<br />\n<br />\n歡迎有興趣朋友 <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MmqsdxQcR6lrp_4Jw9uMqw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMmqsdxQcR6lrp_4Jw9uMqw&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFoMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=1ba7f08a\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/MmqsdxQcR6lrp_4Jw9uMqw</a> 加入成為小器鬼<br />\n<br />\n而8月5號小器嘅大家，識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5d6f803d20e1f313cb0912ce6b46b661d86b64","tid":1391590,"uid":266022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:20:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae914c9a899f4bcd01986eba4737f32ac5810cd9","tid":1391590,"uid":27780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:21:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97669a89ab046826ca0e32b282dda9f9a07a7fe","tid":1391590,"uid":64938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:21:49.000Z","msg":"[香城online]傳令兵的技巧和心得<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382782</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n就快又發夢啦，手足幫手廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset